  /// Multiple sectors may share the same Secullum departamento (N:1).
  secullumDepartamentoId Int?
  /// Secullum integration: default Horario.Id used when creating funcionários
  /// for users in this sector. Bridge falls back to this when the user has
  /// no per-user override. NULL = no default (bridge uses HorarioId=1).
  secullumHorarioId      Int?
